144
00:07:54,016 --> 00:07:55,017
<i>Isn't that right?</i>

145
00:07:55,768 --> 00:07:57,269
<i>He's been watching everything!</i>

146
00:07:58,104 --> 00:07:59,480
If you aren't Kira...

147
00:07:59,939 --> 00:08:03,192
