can directly contact Kira...

148
00:08:03,609 --> 00:08:04,694
<i>then let's make a deal.</i>

149
00:08:05,194 --> 00:08:06,237
<i>A deal?!</i>

150
00:08:06,988 --> 00:08:11,867
<i>Delay the death of E.L.F.'s president
and Mr. Zenzai one month.</i>

151
00:08:12,410 --> 00:08:15,162
<i>This shouldn't be difficult for you.</i>

152
00:08:16,038 --> 00:08:18,290
- Yes, I see...
- If we want to randomize the deaths...

153
00:08:18,499 --> 00:08:19,959
- Yes... Go on...
- just throw darts at a calendar.

154
00:08:20,334 --> 00:08:21,502
If you do this,

155
00:08:21,794 --> 00:08:26,298
and cooperate with us from now on,
your crime. . .no...

156
00:08:26,799 --> 00:08:29,051
<i>everyone other than
Kira will not be charged...</i>

157
00:08:29,176 --> 00:08:31,095
<i>under the belief that they were
threatened by Kira</i>

