00:08:31,262 --> 00:08:32,596
<i>into participating in the meetings.</i>

159
00:08:33,472 --> 00:08:34,890
Ah...lsee...

160
00:08:35,975 --> 00:08:37,435
<i>My only option is join L.</i>

161
00:08:37,727 --> 00:08:40,896
<i>No, I'll be killed if Kira finds out
that I've sided with L.</i>

162
00:08:41,439 --> 00:08:42,523
<i>What should I do?</i>

163
00:08:42,732 --> 00:08:45,401
If you reveal this conversation,
it'll cause a panic.

164
00:08:46,318 --> 00:08:47,570
There would be no advantage for you.

165
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,947
Everyone will be caught.

166
00:08:50,781 --> 00:08:53,784
But my goal is to go
one-on-one against Kira.

167
00:08:54,702 --> 00:08:58,247
<i>Listen... If L wins against Kira,
you'll be acquitted.</i>

168
00:08:58,831 --> 00:09:02,251
<i>If Kira wins against me,
you'll carry on with your luxurious life.</i>

169
00:09:03,502 --> 00:09:07,298
<i>Or you can remain a spectator and
g0 along with either side.</i>

170
00:09:08,215 --> 00:09:11,927
