such morbid things?

207
00:11:01,287 --> 00:11:03,873
We have a month to figure out
Kira's identity

208
00:11:03,998 --> 00:11:05,833
and gather evidence against him.

209
00:11:06,709 --> 00:11:07,793
The challenge is just beginning.

210
00:11:08,127 --> 00:11:09,170
Yes...

211
00:11:09,795 --> 00:11:12,798
But you're the one who
first noticed Yotsuba.

212
00:11:13,340 --> 00:11:16,135
You may be more capable than I am.

213
00:11:17,469 --> 00:11:19,597
You might be able to do it.

214
00:11:21,265 --> 00:11:23,309
If I die...

215
00:11:25,019 --> 00:11:26,896
would you take over for me as L?

216
00:11:43,454 --> 00:11:45,956
If I die, would you take over for me?

217
00:11:46,832 --> 00:11:47,875
As L.

218
00:11:49,418 --> 00:11:52,421
<i>If this is all an act and he is Kira,
he's sure to say yes...</i>

219
00:11:54,006 --> 00:11:55,341
What are you talking about, Ryuzaki?

220
00:11:55,925 --> 00:11:58,844
As long as we have this,
won't we die together?

221
