I get it...

222
00:12:03,265 --> 00:12:04,308
Sorry Ryuzaki...

223
00:12:04,516 --> 00:12:08,395
I'm going to tell everyone
what you're thinking.

224
00:12:10,231 --> 00:12:12,566
Ryuzaki thinks that if I'm Kira,

225
00:12:12,900 --> 00:12:17,404
I'm eitherjust pretending I'm not him
and putting on an act...

226
00:12:17,696 --> 00:12:19,907
