And that L brought her in
for questioning

333
00:17:57,995 --> 00:18:00,289
because he suspected that
she was the Second Kira.

334
00:18:01,415 --> 00:18:02,583
Well, that <i>£9</i> true.

335
00:18:03,166 --> 00:18:06,503
If they know that Misa Amane
might know L...

336
